Defendant in custody.   
Defendant is before the Court for sentencing, his probation having been revoked effective 04-06-17.   
Defendant is sentenced to the Wisconsin State Prison System for a total sentence of eight (8) years.   Four (4) years initial confinement, followed by four (4) years extended supervision.   Conditions of extended supervision are:
1) Sex offender treatment and follow through;
2) Maintain full-time employment/schooling combination; 
3) No contact with any victim; 
4) Other than work related or family members, no contact with anyone under age 18;
5) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC; 
6) AODA assessment and follow through counseling.  
Defendant is entitled to 412 days sentence credit.  
Defendant is not eligible for the Challenge Incarceration Program nor the Substance Abuse Program.  
